 wheat flour. It is rather chewy in consistency and absorbs a lot of flavour from the things it is cooked with. It is mainly used for preparing the moghrabieh dish, a traditional dish in Lebanon."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","1h 25m","6 portions"]}